{
  "stem": "18520.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] If somebody died in the ghetto, there was nobody to take you, nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father or my brother or the other, what happened with him is they come with a wagon, and people pushed it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a [NON-ENGLISH], a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People used to leave it outside on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People used to hide this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you want-- if you lived in the, the beginning--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the buildings, and they had a hall for cold winter, to have some food fresh, they had halls.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What you call this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], cellars, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and they used to hide them to get the ration, the bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have a card.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And each time they ripped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I get more bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So if they find out, the police, they beat you to death.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They filled up with 10 people, 20 people, whatever they can push.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ghetto was built.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They closed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They closed the ghetto in 1940.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It took them almost-- since they, they taking over-- they took over the ghetto, they, they built the ghetto, put concrete poles and everything--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Around it, and when they finished it, they finished at the end of '44, '40, '40.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put electric in, high power.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You touched it, you're gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outside they had tall--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, towers around it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They supposed to keep the, the, the, the order in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They dealt with dead people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe what they knew, maybe relatives.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you saw them as an animal, as a wild person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't think that this is even a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They act even like not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
